$ PowerShell: the preference variable $OFS

The → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/preference[preference] variable `$OFS` contains the *output field separator* which specifies the string that with which elements
of an → Windows/PowerShell/language/type/array[array] are joined when converted to a string.

